{"tid":1384540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葉國謙：相信林鄭會在施政報告作出交代","createTime":"2019-07-30T02:04:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T04:26:00.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"43a51cef1c62b20276e4dd42fac3b995348d2d86","tid":1384540,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:04:20.000Z","msg":"行政會議非官守成員、港區全國人大代表葉國謙表示，特首林鄭月娥已盡可能就社會訴求作出回應，現時要思考如何解決社會矛盾，相信她在即將公布的《施政報告》須作出交代。<br />\n<br />\n至於有公務員舉辦反修例集會、有政務官亦發出聯署聲明，葉國謙就指出，政府需要就此檢討，但相信參與的只是少部分人，不代表政府眾叛親離。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2203896/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2203896%2F&d=HYT0XJgSPTYEb9NwUTCrmpmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=4b75d023\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2203896/</a>"},{"pid":"0c515d0e18347ae8f21952dd11c77fc6936ed433","tid":1384540,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:05:35.000Z","msg":"第二位行會成員覺得林鄭會用施政報告拆局"},{"pid":"4dd141540e46bf69d61577e840b8c04b7449374d","tid":1384540,"uid":4496,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:06:16.000Z","msg":"施政報告得黎老解都接管左啦"},{"pid":"e13708edc3c539defdcf25463e659c20389f8cd7","tid":1384540,"uid":134321,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:06:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4dd9b86ff10efbbf0fc8a1dea38d2468c350a3c2","tid":1384540,"uid":23707,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:06:55.000Z","msg":"喂葉國謙含撚啦屌你老母 扮傻"},{"pid":"22a7b1ab575cb45ec2906a87a8f06015dc75464e","tid":1384540,"uid":66113,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:07:41.000Z","msg":"葉公公呢D仆街冚又係正宗賣隊友<br />\n成個民建聯呢排都已經少出聲佢又走出黎撥火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /